elect> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph&nbsp; C</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-20\" data-qnumber=\"20\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">vii</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-20\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-20\" data-qnumber=\"20\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(20,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">In highlighted sentences, we can see that this paragraph talks about the resident that would not require automobiles.\nHeading vii - An urban plan to reduce traffic - is the only heading that mention about traffic - automobiles.\nSo, Heading vii is the correct answer.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">4.</span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"21\" name=\"question-4\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph&nbsp; D</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-21\" data-qnumber=\"21\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">iv</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-21\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-21\" data-qnumber=\"21\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(21,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">In the first sentence of this paragraph, it talks about the stock market crash - means financial problems - and then, it leads to the creation of three towns.\nHeading iv is the correct answer because it mentions all about the financial crisis and the creation of three towns (spread an urban planning concept)</div></div></div></div>\n', 4, 2, 4, 3, 1, '2017-10-26 16:50:07', '2017-11-06 08:54:08');
