%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph E</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-26\" data-qnumber=\"26\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">vi</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-26\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-26\" data-qnumber=\"26\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(26,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">This paragraph concerns reference books, which are an certain kind of books that cannot be taken out of the library - heading vi is the correct heading for this paragraph.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">6. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-6 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"27\" name=\"question-6\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option><option value=\"viii\">viii</option><option value=\"ix\">ix</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph F</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-6 explain-area-27\" data-qnumber=\"27\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 6 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">ii</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-27\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-27\" data-qnumber=\"27\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(27,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">The last question of this paragraph leads us to the heading ii.\nThis paragraph can be disturbed by heading ix - the way books were arranged, however, this paragraph describes nothing about \"similary ways\" - there is no comparison here.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">7. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"28\" name=\"question-7\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option><option value=\"viii\">viii</option><option value=\"ix\">ix</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph G</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-7 explain-area-28\" data-qnumber=\"28\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 7 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">iii</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-28\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-28\" data-qnumber=\"28\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(28,7)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\