ge-pill key-answer\">viii</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-30\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-30\" data-qnumber=\"30\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(30,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">It is clear that this paragraph talks about family size - educated girls tend to have smaller family size (fewer children). So, heading viii is the correct answer.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">3. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"31\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option><option value=\"viii\">viii</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Section C </span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-31\" data-qnumber=\"31\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">iv</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-31\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-31\" data-qnumber=\"31\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(31,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">This paragraph describes the costs that fami