rofessional drivers, though consumers will have more money to spend on other things, creating employment in those areas. </span></span></span></p>\n\n                                ', NULL, '<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Which paragraphs contain the following information? </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">1. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"82\" name=\"question-1\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option><option value=\"H\">H</option><option value=\"I\">I</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It is predicted that many lives will be saved. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">2. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"83\" name=\"question-2\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option><option value=\"H\">H</option><option value=\"I\">I</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Prototypes have already been tested successful