ragraph, it indicates that aim of ecotourism is to educate traveller, not local communities.\n- Answer C is the correct answer. you can find the information in highlighted sentence.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>2. However, ecotourism can cause problems when</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"129\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span class=\"fontstyle01\" new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">the local population does not welcome visitors.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"129\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span class=\"fontstyle01\" new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">extra facilities and amenities are required to cope with a population increase.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p s