-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(135,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">Keywrod: Goldilocks\n------------\n- A is wrong, because in this paragraph, you can see that Goldilocks zone only has the probability of being habitable.\n- B &amp; C provice unclear information about this zone.\n- D is the correct answer, you can find those information clearly in highlighted sentence.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n', 2, 4, 6, 3, 1, '2017-11-06 15:05:39', '2017-11-07 09:03:33');
