es=\"\">People may die quickly in the water of polar regions. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></pre>\n\n<pre style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Looking for food is the first thing to do mast of the time. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Survivors after a flood won \'t need water for drinking.</span></span></span></span><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-143\" data-qnumber=\"143\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">B</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-143\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-143\" data-qnumber=\"143\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(143,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">- A is wrong, based on the second paragraph, exposure to wind can be