een decades ago.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-1 \" data-qnumber=\"144\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A few decades ago.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-1 \" data-qnumber=\"144\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">30 years ago.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"144\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">There is no information about it.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><b>Twin engine turboprop could carry:</b></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"145\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman