xplanation(172,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">The first sentence of fifth paragraph provides this information.\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">6. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-6 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"173\" name=\"question-6\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Sometimes those circumstances that are not threatening to us are also stressful.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-6 explain-area-173\" data-qnumber=\"173\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 6 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">FALSE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-173\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-173\" data-qnumber=\"173\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(173,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">The answer can be found in last sentence of sixth paragraph.\nThis statement will be true if it said that: sometimes those circumstances that are not threatening to us ARE NOT STREESFUL</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">7. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"174\" name=\"question-7\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">An event or situation may not always be a stressor.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-7 explain-area-174\" data-qnumber=\"174\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 7 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-174\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-174\" data-qnumber=\"174\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(174,7)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">Last paragraph expalins this idea quite clearly.</div></div></div></div>\n', 7, 4, 7, 3, 1, '2017-11-07 11:10:45', '2017-11-08 14:08:06');
