rs further north live bowhead whales. To survive in these frosty, remote waters they have a layer of blubber almost half a metre thick</span>. In his studies, Dr. Craig George found blubber mass ranged from 43% to 50% of the body mass of yearling whales.</span></span></span></p>\n\n                                ', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Answer the questions with <b>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS</b>:</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b><span style=\"color:black\">Which animal has the most fat?&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b></span></span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>1</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"250\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" /></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\">\n	<p style=\"margin-left:.25in; text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b><span style=\"color:black\">How is called tissue of marine mammals that is rich with fat?&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b></span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>2</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"251\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" /></p>\n	</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\">\n	<p style=\"margin-left:.25in; text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span ne