><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">Keywrod: shortest time\n-------------\nThis question asks about one of criteria for volunteers. So, when you answer this question, you need to find out it in paragraph 2.\nIn highlighted sentence, we can see that they mention about time - 2 years.\nSo, answer for this question is two years.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">5... Which languages are given as an example of what can benefit volunteers?&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>5</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"266\" name=\"question-5\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" disabled=\"disabled\"></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-266\" data-qnumber=\"266\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"11\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">French and Spanish</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-266\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-266\" data-qnumber=\"266\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(266,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">Those information can be found in last sentence of this passage.</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n', 5, 4, 11, 3, 1, '2017-11-10 13:45:17', '2017-11-13 13:49:32');
